 31/7/16 . Commenc our " Rest ? " with the usual syllabus of infantri train . Our act O.C. is not popular , so thing are not as pleasant as they might be . It is veri pleasant here surround by wood and a small river run past . August 5th . 1916 . Have been drill hard all the week . Went on a long rout march today . Old " Digbi " came back this morn he look none the wors for his shell shock . We gave him a cheer for we are all pleas to see him back . There a two veri nice old French peopl in this billet , their daughter is veri nice too . I am well in with them , and often take " coffe royal " with them . Was issu with a shirt and receiv a lot of mail this week .
